`AgentRuntimeKind`, `AgentRuntimeListKind`, `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind`\n40:   - Define `CodeInterpreterKind`, `CodeInterpreterListKind`, `CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind`\n41:   - Define `SchemeGroupVersion` and `Resource()` helper function\n42:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n43: \n44: - [ ] **T2.4** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n45:   - Define `TargetPort` struct with fields: `PathPrefix`, `Name`, `Port`, `Protocol`\n46:   - Define `AuthModeType` type alias and constants: `AuthModePicoD`, `AuthModeNone`\n47:   - Define `ProtocolType` type alias and constants: `ProtocolTypeHTTP`, `ProtocolTypeHTTPS`\n48:   - Add appropriate kubebuilder validation markers\n49:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n50: \n51: - [ ] **T2.5** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n52:   - Define `AgentRuntime` struct with markers:\n53:     - `+genclient`\n54:     - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n55:     - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n56:     - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n57:     - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`\n58:     - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n59:   - Define `AgentRuntimeSpec` with fields: `Ports`, `Template`, `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`\n60:   - Define `AgentRuntimeStatus` with field: `Conditions`\n61:   - Define `SandboxTemplate` struct with fields: `Labels`, `Annotations`, `Spec`\n62:   - Define `AgentRuntimeList` struct with appropriate markers\n63:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n64: \n65: - [ ] **T2.6** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n66:   - Define `CodeInterpreter` struct with markers:\n67:     - `+genclient`\n68:     - `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n69:     - `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n70:     - `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n71:     - `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`\n72:     - `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n73:   - Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` with fields: `Ports`, `Template`, `SessionTimeout`, `MaxSessionDuration`, `WarmPoolSize`, `AuthMode`\n74:   - Define `CodeInterpreterStatus` with fields: `Conditions`, `Ready`\n75:   - Define `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` struct with all fields from design\n76:   - Define `CodeInterpreterList` struct with appropriate markers\n77:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n78: \n79: ### Phase 3: Code Generation\n80: \n81: - [ ] **T3.1** Run `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` to generate DeepCopy methods\n82:   - Verify: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` file created\n83:   - Verify: All types implement `runtime.Object` interface\n84: \n85: - [ ] **T3.2** Run `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`\n86:   - Verify: CRD YAML files generated for `agentruntimes` and `codeinterpreters`\n87: \n88: - [ ] **T3.3** Run `client-gen` to generate client-go code\n89:   - Output to `client-go/` directory\n90:   - Verify: `clientset/`, `informers/`, `listers/` directories created\n91: \n92: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n93: \n94: - [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n95:   - Test DeepCopy for `AgentRuntime` (verify deep copy of all fields)\n96:   - Test DeepCopy for `CodeInterpreter` (verify deep copy of all fields)\n97:   - Test default values applied correctly (`sessionTimeout=15m`, `maxSessionDuration=8h`, `authMode=picod`)\n98:   - Test enum validation for `AuthModeType` and `ProtocolType`\n99:   - Test JSON serialization/deserialization for all types\n100:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n101: \n102: ### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n103: \n104: - [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n105:   - Fix any issues reported\n106: \n107: - [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n108:   - Fix any linting issues\n109: \n110: - [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase for all struct fields\n111:   - Check: `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`\n112:   - Check: `pathPrefix`, `imagePullPolicy`, `imagePullSecrets`\n113: \n114: - [ ] **T5.4** Verify Kubernetes API conventions compliance\n115:   - All required fields have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n116:   - Optional fields have `+optional` marker\n117:   - Default values specified with `+kubebuilder:default=...`\n118: \n119: ### Phase 6: Documentation\n120: \n121: - [ ] **T6.1** Add godoc comments to all exported types and fields\n122: - [ ] **T6.2** Verify package-level documentation in `doc.go` describes the API group purpose\n123: \n124: ---\n125: \n126: ## Task Dependencies\n127: \n128: ```\n129: T1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3 → T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3 → T2.4 → T2.5 → T2.6\n130:                                                             ↓\n131:                                                           T3.1 → T3.2 → T3.3\n132:                                                                             ↓\n133:                                                                           T4.1\n134:                                                                             ↓\n135:                                                      T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3 → T5.4\n136:                                                                             ↓\n137:                                                                           T6.1 → T6.2\n138: ```\n139: \n140: ---\n141: \n142: ## Verification Commands\n143: \n144: | Task | Verification Command |\n145: |------|----------------------|\n146: | T1.3 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n147: | T2.1-T2.6 | `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n148: | T3.1 | `test -f pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n149: | T3.2 | `test -f manifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` |\n150: | T3.3 | `test -d client-go/clientset` |\n151: | T4.1 | `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v -cover` |\n152: | T5.1 | `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n153: | T5.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` |\n154: \n155: ---\n156: \n157: ## Acceptance Criteria\n158: \n159: - [ ] All types defined per design.md specification\n160: - [ ] JSON tags use camelCase\n161: - [ ] Complete field comments for all exported types\n162: - [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n163: - [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n164: - [ ] DeepCopy methods generated and functional\n165: - [ ] CRD YAML files generated successfully\n166: - [ ] client-go code generated successfully\n167: - [ ] Unit tests pass with >80% coverage\n168: \n169: ---\n170: \n171: ## Notes\n172: \n173: - Follow Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n174: - Use controller-tools v0.17.2 for code generation\n175: - Reference implementation path (if available): `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n(End of file - total 175 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- [ ] **T1.2** Initialize Go module if not exists (`go.mod` with `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775840950701,"end":1775840950729}}}}
