{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840964002,"sessionID":"ses_287a1f553ffehb5F57PYo0UhiM","part":{"id":"prt_d785ea538001BnVNipPnBEgYHR","messageID":"msg_d785e7a17001fNl5tmCtYxVCEI","sessionID":"ses_287a1f553ffehb5F57PYo0UhiM","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-abb897fd2ebb4f939b89cdd29c998ab7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，供 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 使用。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: 共享类型和常量定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 类型定义使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 常量使用统一命名规范（LabelKey*, AnnotationKey*, ConditionType*）\n22: - 默认值常量供 controller 使用\n23: - 所有定义位于 `shared_types.go`，便于集中管理\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | (无外部依赖) | 共享类型为基础定义 |\n30: \n31: ### Controller-gen Markers\n32: \n33: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n34: |--------|------------|---------|\n35: | `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum` | ProtocolType, AuthModeType | 枚举验证 |\n36: | `+kubebuilder:default` | TargetPort.Protocol | 默认值 |\n37: \n38: ## Data Structures\n39: \n40: ### Shared Types\n41: \n42: #### ProtocolType\n43: \n44: ```go\n45: // ProtocolType defines the protocol for a target port.\n46: // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n47: type ProtocolType string\n48: \n49: const (\n50:     // ProtocolTypeHTTP indicates HTTP protocol.\n51:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n52:     // ProtocolTypeHTTPS indicates HTTPS protocol.\n53:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n54: )\n55: ```\n56: \n57: #### AuthModeType\n58: \n59: ```go\n60: // AuthModeType defines the authentication mode for a CodeInterpreter.\n61: // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n62: type AuthModeType string\n63: \n64: const (\n65:     // AuthModePicoD indicates pico authentication mode.\n66:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n67:     // AuthModeNone indicates no authentication.\n68:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n69: )\n70: ```\n71: \n72: #### TargetPort\n73: \n74: ```go\n75: // TargetPort defines a network port configuration for exposing sandbox services.\n76: type TargetPort struct {\n77:     // PathPrefix is the URL path prefix for routing to this port.\n78:     // +optional\n79:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n80: \n81:     // Name is a human-readable name for this port.\n82:     // +optional\n83:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n84: \n85:     // Port is the container port number to expose.\n86:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n87: \n88:     // Protocol specifies the protocol for this port (HTTP or HTTPS).\n89:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n90:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n91:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n92: }\n93: ```\n94: \n95: ### Constants\n96: \n97: #### Label Constants\n98: \n99: Labels 用于标识沙箱资源的元数据，遵循 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/<key>` 格式：\n100: \n101: ```go\n102: const (\n103:     // LabelKeyOwnerRuntime indicates the owning AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter name.\n104:     LabelKeyOwnerRuntime = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\"\n105: \n106:     // LabelKeyOwnerKind indicates the owning CRD kind (AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter).\n107:     LabelKeyOwnerKind = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind\"\n108: \n109:     // LabelKeySessionID indicates the active session identifier.\n110:     LabelKeySessionID = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\"\n111: \n112:     // LabelKeySandboxType indicates the sandbox type (agent/code-interpreter).\n113:     LabelKeySandboxType = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type\"\n114: \n115:     // LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent indicates an agent sandbox.\n116:     LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent = \"agent\"\n117: \n118:     // LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter indicates a code interpreter sandbox.\n119:     LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter = \"code-interpreter\"\n120: )\n121: ```\n122: \n123: #### Annotation Constants\n124: \n125: Annotations 用于存储运行时配置和状态信息：\n126: \n127: ```go\n128: const (\n129:     // AnnotationKeyAuthMode stores the authentication mode for the sandbox.\n130:     AnnotationKeyAuthMode = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode\"\n131: \n132:     // AnnotationKeySessionStart stores the session start timestamp.\n133:     AnnotationKeySessionStart = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start\"\n134: \n135:     // AnnotationKeySessionEnd stores the session end timestamp.\n136:     AnnotationKeySessionEnd = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end\"\n137: \n138:     // AnnotationKeyLastActivity stores the last activity timestamp.\n139:     AnnotationKeyLastActivity = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n140: \n141:     // AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember indicates if pod is part of warm pool.\n142:     AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member\"\n143: )\n144: ```\n145: \n146: #### Condition Type Constants\n147: \n148: Condition types 用于 status.conditions 数组，遵循 Kubernetes Condition pattern：\n149: \n150: ```go\n151: const (\n152:     // ConditionTypeReady indicates the runtime is ready to accept sessions.\n153:     ConditionTypeReady = \"Ready\"\n154: \n155:     // ConditionTypeAvailable indicates the runtime is available for use.\n156:     ConditionTypeAvailable = \"Available\"\n157: \n158:     // ConditionTypeProgressing indicates the runtime is being created/updated.\n159:     ConditionTypeProgressing = \"Progressing\"\n160: \n161:     // ConditionTypeDegraded indicates the runtime is in a degraded state.\n162:     ConditionTypeDegraded = \"Degraded\"\n163: \n164:     // ConditionTypeSessionActive indicates an active session is running.\n165:     ConditionTypeSessionActive = \"SessionActive\"\n166: )\n167: ```\n168: \n169: #### Condition Reason Constants\n170: \n171: Condition reasons 描述 condition 状态变化的原因：\n172: \n173: ```go\n174: const (\n175:     // ConditionReasonRunning indicates the runtime is running normally.\n176:     ConditionReasonRunning = \"Running\"\n177: \n178:     // ConditionReasonCreating indicates the runtime is being created.\n179:     ConditionReasonCreating = \"Creating\"\n180: \n181:     // ConditionReasonUpdating indicates the runtime is being updated.\n182:     ConditionReasonUpdating = \"Updating\"\n183: \n184:     // ConditionReasonDeleting indicates the runtime is being deleted.\n185:     ConditionReasonDeleting = \"Deleting\"\n186: \n187:     // ConditionReasonError indicates an error occurred.\n188:     ConditionReasonError = \"Error\"\n189: \n190:     // ConditionReasonTimeout indicates a timeout occurred.\n191:     ConditionReasonTimeout = \"Timeout\"\n192: \n193:     // ConditionReasonSessionStarted indicates a session has started.\n194:     ConditionReasonSessionStarted = \"SessionStarted\"\n195: \n196:     // ConditionReasonSessionEnded indicates a session has ended.\n197:     ConditionReasonSessionEnded = \"SessionEnded\"\n198: \n199:     // ConditionReasonIdleTimeout indicates session ended due to idle timeout.\n200:     ConditionReasonIdleTimeout = \"IdleTimeout\"\n201: \n202:     // ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached indicates session ended due to max duration.\n203:     ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached = \"MaxDurationReached\"\n204: )\n205: ```\n206: \n207: #### Default Value Constants\n208: \n209: 默认值常量供 controller 初始化配置使用：\n210: \n211: ```go\n212: const (\n213:     // DefaultSessionTimeout is the default idle session timeout (15 minutes).\n214:     DefaultSessionTimeout = 15 * time.Minute\n215: \n216:     // DefaultMaxSessionDuration is the default maximum session duration (8 hours).\n217:     DefaultMaxSessionDuration = 8 * time.Hour\n218: \n219:     // DefaultWarmPoolSize is the default warm pool size for CodeInterpreter.\n220:     DefaultWarmPoolSize = 0\n221: \n222:     // DefaultAuthMode is the default authentication mode.\n223:     DefaultAuthMode = AuthModePicoD\n224: \n225:     // DefaultProtocol is the default protocol for TargetPort.\n226:     DefaultProtocol = ProtocolTypeHTTP\n227: )\n228: ```\n229: \n230: ## API Contracts\n231: \n232: ### Label Contract\n233: \n234: | Label Key | Value Format | Applied To |\n235: |-----------|--------------|------------|\n236: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime` | CR name | Pod, Service |\n237: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind` | `AgentRuntime` / `CodeInterpreter` | Pod, Service |\n238: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id` | UUID | Pod (active session) |\n239: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type` | `agent` / `code-interpreter` | Pod |\n240: \n241: ### Annotation Contract\n242: \n243: | Annotation Key | Value Format | Applied To |\n244: |-----------------|--------------|------------|\n245: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode` | `picod` / `none` | Pod |\n246: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n247: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n248: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity` | RFC3339 timestamp | Pod |\n249: | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member` | `true` / `false` | Pod |\n250: \n251: ### Condition Contract\n252: \n253: | Condition Type | Meaning | True Condition |\n254: |-----------------|---------|----------------|\n255: | `Ready` | Runtime ready for sessions | Pod running, no errors |\n256: | `Available` | Runtime available | Ready + healthy |\n257: | `Progressing` | Runtime being modified | Creation/update in progress |\n258: | `Degraded` | Runtime in degraded state | Errors present |\n259: | `SessionActive` | Session running | Pod has active session |\n260: \n261: ## Error Handling\n262: \n263: ### Validation Errors\n264: \n265: | Error Type | Trigger | Response |\n266: |------------|---------|----------|\n267: | Invalid ProtocolType | Value not `HTTP`/`HTTPS` | API server rejects with 400 |\n268: | Invalid AuthModeType | Value not `picod`/`none` | API server rejects with 400 |\n269: | Missing required Port | Port field empty | API server rejects with 400 |\n270: | Invalid port number | Port > 65535 | Controller webhook rejects |\n271: \n272: ### Controller Error Handling\n273: \n274: | Error Type | Handling |\n275: |------------|----------|\n276: | Label/Annotation conflict | Log warning, use CR-specified value |\n277: | Condition update failure | Retry with exponential backoff |\n278: | Default value override | Use CR spec value if specified |\n279: \n280: ## Testing Strategy\n281: \n282: ### Unit Tests\n283: \n284: | Test Category | Coverage |\n285: |---------------|----------|\n286: | Enum constants | Verify all enum values match expected strings |\n287: | DeepCopy | TargetPort.DeepCopy creates independent copy |\n288: | JSON serialization | TargetPort JSON tags correct (camelCase) |\n289: | Default values | Verify default constants match spec defaults |\n290: \n291: ### Test Cases\n292: \n293: ```go\n294: func TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n295:     tests := []struct {\n296:         name     string\n297:         constant ProtocolType\n298:         expected string\n299:     }{\n300:         {\"HTTP\", ProtocolTypeHTTP, \"HTTP\"},\n301:         {\"HTTPS\", ProtocolTypeHTTPS, \"HTTPS\"},\n302:     }\n303:     for _, tt := range tests {\n304:         if tt.constant != tt.expected {\n305:             t.Errorf(\"%s: expected %s, got %s\", tt.name, tt.expected, tt.constant)\n306:         }\n307:     }\n308: }\n309: \n310: func TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n311:     tests := []struct {\n312:         name     string\n313:         constant AuthModeType\n314:         expected string\n315:     }{\n316:         {\"PicoD\", AuthModePicoD, \"picod\"},\n317:         {\"None\", AuthModeNone, \"none\"},\n318:     }\n319:     for _, tt := range tests {\n320:         if tt.constant != tt.expected {\n321:             t.Errorf(\"%s: expected %s, got %s\", tt.name, tt.expected, tt.constant)\n322:         }\n323:     }\n324: }\n325: \n326: func TestTargetPortDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n327:     original := &TargetPort{\n328:         PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n329:         Name:       \"api\",\n330:         Port:       8080,\n331:         Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n332:     }\n333:     copy := original.DeepCopy()\n334:     \n335:     if copy == original {\n336:         t.Error(\"DeepCopy returned same pointer\")\n337:     }\n338:     if copy.PathPrefix != original.PathPrefix {\n339:         t.Error(\"PathPrefix not copied correctly\")\n340:     }\n341:     \n342:     copy.PathPrefix = \"/modified\"\n343:     if original.PathPrefix == \"/modified\" {\n344:         t.Error(\"DeepCopy is not deep\")\n345:     }\n346: }\n347: \n348: func TestTargetPortJSONSerialization(t *testing.T) {\n349:     tp := TargetPort{\n350:         PathPrefix: \"/api\",\n351:         Name:       \"api\",\n352:         Port:       8080,\n353:         Protocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n354:     }\n355:     data, err := json.Marshal(tp)\n356:     if err != nil {\n357:         t.Fatalf(\"marshal failed: %v\", err)\n358:     }\n359:     expected := `{\"pathPrefix\":\"/api\",\"name\":\"api\",\"port\":8080,\"protocol\":\"HTTP\"}`\n360:     if string(data) != expected {\n361:         t.Errorf(\"expected %s, got %s\", expected, string(data))\n362:     }\n363: }\n364: \n365: func TestLabelConstants(t *testing.T) {\n366:     if LabelKeyOwnerRuntime != \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\" {\n367:         t.Error(\"LabelKeyOwnerRuntime mismatch\")\n368:     }\n369:     if LabelKeySessionID != \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\" {\n370:         t.Error(\"LabelKeySessionID mismatch\")\n371:     }\n372: }\n373: \n374: func TestConditionTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n375:     if ConditionTypeReady != \"Ready\" {\n376:         t.Error(\"ConditionTypeReady mismatch\")\n377:     }\n378:     if ConditionTypeAvailable != \"Available\" {\n379:         t.Error(\"ConditionTypeAvailable mismatch\")\n380:     }\n381: }\n382: \n383: func TestDefaultConstants(t *testing.T) {\n384:     if DefaultSessionTimeout != 15*time.Minute {\n385:         t.Error(\"DefaultSessionTimeout mismatch\")\n386:     }\n387:     if DefaultMaxSessionDuration != 8*time.Hour {\n388:         t.Error(\"DefaultMaxSessionDuration mismatch\")\n389:     }\n390:     if DefaultAuthMode != AuthModePicoD {\n391:         t.Error(\"DefaultAuthMode mismatch\")\n392:     }\n393:     if DefaultProtocol != ProtocolTypeHTTP {\n394:         t.Error(\"DefaultProtocol mismatch\")\n395:     }\n396: }\n397: ```\n398: \n399: ### Integration Tests\n400: \n401: - Verify labels/annotations applied to pods match constant definitions\n402: - Verify conditions in CRD status use defined type constants\n403: - Verify CRD YAML generation includes enum validation\n404: \n405: ## File Structure\n406: \n407: ```\n408: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n409:   shared_types.go      — 共享类型、枚举、常量定义\n410:   zz_generated.deepcopy.go — DeepCopy 方法（由 controller-gen 生成）\n411:   types_test.go        — 单元测试\n412: ```\n413: \n414: ### shared_types.go Structure\n415: \n416: ```go\n417: package v1alpha1\n418: \n419: import \"time\"\n420: \n421: // ============================================================================\n422: // Type Definitions\n423: // ============================================================================\n424: \n425: type ProtocolType string\n426: const (\n427:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n428:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n429: )\n430: \n431: type AuthModeType string\n432: const (\n433:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n434:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n435: )\n436: \n437: type TargetPort struct {\n438:     PathPrefix string      `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n439:     Name       string      `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n440:     Port       uint32      `json:\"port\"`\n441:     Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n442: }\n443: \n444: // ============================================================================\n445: // Label Constants\n446: // ============================================================================\n447: \n448: const (\n449:     LabelKeyOwnerRuntime     = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-runtime\"\n450:     LabelKeyOwnerKind        = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/owner-kind\"\n451:     LabelKeySessionID        = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-id\"\n452:     LabelKeySandboxType      = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/sandbox-type\"\n453:     LabelKeySandboxTypeAgent = \"agent\"\n454:     LabelKeySandboxTypeCodeInterpreter = \"code-interpreter\"\n455: )\n456: \n457: // ============================================================================\n458: // Annotation Constants\n459: // ============================================================================\n460: \n461: const (\n462:     AnnotationKeyAuthMode       = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/auth-mode\"\n463:     AnnotationKeySessionStart   = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-start\"\n464:     AnnotationKeySessionEnd     = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/session-end\"\n465:     AnnotationKeyLastActivity   = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n466:     AnnotationKeyWarmPoolMember = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/warm-pool-member\"\n467: )\n468: \n469: // ============================================================================\n470: // Condition Constants\n471: // ============================================================================\n472: \n473: const (\n474:     ConditionTypeReady        = \"Ready\"\n475:     ConditionTypeAvailable    = \"Available\"\n476:     ConditionTypeProgressing  = \"Progressing\"\n477:     ConditionTypeDegraded     = \"Degraded\"\n478:     ConditionTypeSessionActive = \"SessionActive\"\n479: )\n480: \n481: const (\n482:     ConditionReasonRunning            = \"Running\"\n483:     ConditionReasonCreating           = \"Creating\"\n484:     ConditionReasonUpdating           = \"Updating\"\n485:     ConditionReasonDeleting           = \"Deleting\"\n486:     ConditionReasonError              = \"Error\"\n487:     ConditionReasonTimeout            = \"Timeout\"\n488:     ConditionReasonSessionStarted     = \"SessionStarted\"\n489:     ConditionReasonSessionEnded       = \"SessionEnded\"\n490:     ConditionReasonIdleTimeout        = \"IdleTimeout\"\n491:     ConditionReasonMaxDurationReached = \"MaxDurationReached\"\n492: )\n493: \n494: // ============================================================================\n495: // Default Value Constants\n496: // ============================================================================\n497: \n498: const (\n499:     DefaultSessionTimeout     = 15 * time.Minute\n500:     DefaultMaxSessionDuration = 8 * time.Hour\n501:     DefaultWarmPoolSize       = 0\n502: )\n503: \n504: var (\n505:     DefaultAuthMode  = AuthModePicoD\n506:     DefaultProtocol  = ProtocolTypeHTTP\n507: )\n508: ```\n509: \n510: ## Generation Commands\n511: \n512: | Command | Output |\n513: |---------|--------|\n514: | `make generate` | DeepCopy code in `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n515: | `go build ./pkg/apis/...` | Compile verification |\n516: | `go test ./pkg/apis/...` | Unit test execution |\n517: \n518: ## References\n519: \n520: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n521: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n522: - Kubebuilder Book: https://book.kubebuilder.io/\n523: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n524: - AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 524 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，供 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 使用。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n共享类型和常量定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 类型定义使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/design.md","time":{"start":1775840963982,"end":1775840964000}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840964005,"sessionID":"ses_287a1f553ffehb5F57PYo0UhiM","part":{"id":"prt_d785ea90100172vqJV7DJK1160","messageID":"msg_d785e7a17001fNl5tmCtYxVCEI","sessionID":"ses_287a1f553ffehb5F57PYo0UhiM","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-bbea3abf3fd0499dbba49e4cb1dcc567","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-0 |\n12: \n13: ## Scope\n14: \n15: 定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，包括:\n16: - `TargetPort` 类型（端口配置）\n17: - `ProtocolType` 枚举（HTTP/HTTPS）\n18: - `AuthModeType` 枚举（picod/none）\n19: - Label/Annotation 常量\n20: - Condition Type 常量\n21: - 默认值常量\n22: \n23: ## Out of Scope\n24: \n25: - Controller 实现\n26: - Webhook 验证逻辑\n27: - CRD YAML 生成\n28: - client-go 代码生成\n29: \n30: ## Dependencies\n31: \n32: 无外部依赖，为 AR-001、AR-002 提供共享类型。\n33: \n34: ## Deliverables\n35: \n36: | File | Description |\n37: |------|-------------|\n38: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go` | 共享类型和常量定义 |\n39: \n40: ## Acceptance Criteria\n41: \n42: - [ ] 共享类型定义符合 Kubernetes API conventions\n43: - [ ] 常量命名遵循统一命名规范\n44: - [ ] 包含完整的 godoc 注释\n45: - [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n46: - [ ] Enum 验证标记正确\n47: \n48: ## References\n49: \n50: - Kubernetes API Conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n51: - AR-001 Design: `changes/AR-001/design.md`\n52: - AR-002 Design: `changes/AR-002/design.md`\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 CRD 共享类型和常量，包括:\n- `TargetPort` 类型（端口配置）\n- `ProtocolType` 枚举（HTTP/HTTPS）\n- `AuthModeType` 枚举（picod/none）\n- Label/Annotation 常量\n- Condition Type 常量","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-003/spec.md","time":{"start":1775840963985,"end":1775840964003}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775840964019,"sessionID":"ses_287a1f553ffehb5F57PYo0UhiM","part":{"id":"prt_d785ead71001ID3vHWET5SMslL","messageID":"msg_d785e7a17001fNl5tmCtYxVCEI","sessionID":"ses_287a1f553ffehb5F57PYo0UhiM","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-98d1f3bf8316475da832614d81172f3e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package v1alpha1\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"encoding/json\"\n5: \t\"testing\"\n6: \t\"time\"\n7: \n8: \tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n9: \tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n10: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n11: )\n12: \n13: func TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n14: \ttests := []struct {\n15: \t\tname string\n16: \t\tar   *AgentRuntime\n17: \t}{\n18: \t\t{\n19: \t\t\tname: \"nil\",\n20: \t\t\tar:   nil,\n21: \t\t},\n22: \t\t{\n23: \t\t\tname: \"empty\",\n24: \t\t\tar:   &AgentRuntime{},\n25: \t\t},\n26: \t\t{\n27: \t\t\tname: \"empty spec\",\n28: \t\t\tar: &AgentRuntime{\n29: \t\t\t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test\"},\n30: \t\t\t},\n31: \t\t},\n32: \t\t{\n33: \t\t\tname: \"full\",\n34: \t\t\tar: &AgentRuntime{\n35: \t\t\t\tTypeMeta: metav1.TypeMeta{\n36: \t\t\t\t\tKind:       AgentRuntimeKind,\n37: \t\t\t\t\tAPIVersion: GroupVersion.String(),\n38: \t\t\t\t},\n39: \t\t\t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n40: \t\t\t\t\tName:      \"test-agentruntime\",\n41: \t\t\t\t\tNamespace: \"default\",\n42: \t\t\t\t\tLabels: map[string]string{\n43: \t\t\t\t\t\t\"app\": \"test\",\n44: \t\t\t\t\t},\n45: \t\t\t\t\tAnnotations: map[string]string{\n46: \t\t\t\t\t\t\"description\": \"test annotation\",\n47: \t\t\t\t\t},\n48: \t\t\t\t},\n49: \t\t\t\tSpec: AgentRuntimeSpec{\n50: \t\t\t\t\tPorts: []TargetPort{\n51: \t\t\t\t\t\t{\n52: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tPathPrefix: \"/api\",\n53: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tName:       \"api-port\",\n54: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tPort:       8080,\n55: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tProtocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n56: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n57: \t\t\t\t\t},\n58: \t\t\t\t\tTemplate: &SandboxTemplate{\n59: \t\t\t\t\t\tLabels: map[string]string{\n60: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"pod-label\": \"value\",\n61: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n62: \t\t\t\t\t\tAnnotations: map[string]string{\n63: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"pod-annotation\": \"value\",\n64: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n65: \t\t\t\t\t\tSpec: corev1.PodSpec{\n66: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tContainers: []corev1.Container{\n67: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\n68: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tName:  \"container\",\n69: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tImage: \"image:latest\",\n70: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n71: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n72: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n73: \t\t\t\t\t},\n74: \t\t\t\t\tSessionTimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 15 * time.Minute},\n75: \t\t\t\t\tMaxSessionDuration: &metav1.Duration{Duration: 8 * time.Hour},\n76: \t\t\t\t},\n77: \t\t\t\tStatus: AgentRuntimeStatus{\n78: \t\t\t\t\tConditions: []metav1.Condition{\n79: \t\t\t\t\t\t{\n80: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tType:   \"Ready\",\n81: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tStatus: metav1.ConditionTrue,\n82: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n83: \t\t\t\t\t},\n84: \t\t\t\t},\n85: \t\t\t},\n86: \t\t},\n87: \t}\n88: \n89: \tfor _, tt := range tests {\n90: \t\tt.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n91: \t\t\tcopy := tt.ar.DeepCopy()\n92: \t\t\tif tt.ar == nil {\n93: \t\t\t\tif copy != nil {\n94: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected nil, got non-nil\")\n95: \t\t\t\t}\n96: \t\t\t\treturn\n97: \t\t\t}\n98: \t\t\tif copy == nil {\n99: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected non-nil, got nil\")\n100: \t\t\t\treturn\n101: \t\t\t}\n102: \t\t\tif copy == tt.ar {\n103: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected different pointer, got same pointer\")\n104: \t\t\t}\n105: \t\t\tif copy.Name != tt.ar.Name {\n106: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Name %s, got %s\", tt.ar.Name, copy.Name)\n107: \t\t\t}\n108: \t\t\tif len(copy.Spec.Ports) != len(tt.ar.Spec.Ports) {\n109: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Ports length %d, got %d\", len(tt.ar.Spec.Ports), len(copy.Spec.Ports))\n110: \t\t\t}\n111: \t\t\tif tt.ar.Spec.SessionTimeout != nil {\n112: \t\t\t\tif copy.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration != tt.ar.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration {\n113: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected SessionTimeout %v, got %v\", tt.ar.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration, copy.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration)\n114: \t\t\t\t}\n115: \t\t\t}\n116: \t\t\tif len(copy.Status.Conditions) != len(tt.ar.Status.Conditions) {\n117: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Conditions length %d, got %d\", len(tt.ar.Status.Conditions), len(copy.Status.Conditions))\n118: \t\t\t}\n119: \t\t\tif tt.ar.Spec.Template != nil && tt.ar.Spec.Template.Labels != nil {\n120: \t\t\t\tif copy.Spec.Template.Labels[\"pod-label\"] != tt.ar.Spec.Template.Labels[\"pod-label\"] {\n121: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Template Labels to match\")\n122: \t\t\t\t}\n123: \t\t\t\tcopy.Spec.Template.Labels[\"pod-label\"] = \"modified\"\n124: \t\t\t\tif tt.ar.Spec.Template.Labels[\"pod-label\"] == \"modified\" {\n125: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"DeepCopy should be deep, modifying copy should not affect original\")\n126: \t\t\t\t}\n127: \t\t\t}\n128: \t\t})\n129: \t}\n130: }\n131: \n132: func TestAgentRuntimeListDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n133: \ttests := []struct {\n134: \t\tname string\n135: \t\tarl  *AgentRuntimeList\n136: \t}{\n137: \t\t{\n138: \t\t\tname: \"nil\",\n139: \t\t\tarl:  nil,\n140: \t\t},\n141: \t\t{\n142: \t\t\tname: \"empty\",\n143: \t\t\tarl:  &AgentRuntimeList{},\n144: \t\t},\n145: \t\t{\n146: \t\t\tname: \"full\",\n147: \t\t\tarl: &AgentRuntimeList{\n148: \t\t\t\tTypeMeta: metav1.TypeMeta{\n149: \t\t\t\t\tKind:       AgentRuntimeListKind,\n150: \t\t\t\t\tAPIVersion: GroupVersion.String(),\n151: \t\t\t\t},\n152: \t\t\t\tListMeta: metav1.ListMeta{},\n153: \t\t\t\tItems: []AgentRuntime{\n154: \t\t\t\t\t{\n155: \t\t\t\t\t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"item1\"},\n156: \t\t\t\t\t},\n157: \t\t\t\t\t{\n158: \t\t\t\t\t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"item2\"},\n159: \t\t\t\t\t},\n160: \t\t\t\t},\n161: \t\t\t},\n162: \t\t},\n163: \t}\n164: \n165: \tfor _, tt := range tests {\n166: \t\tt.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n167: \t\t\tcopy := tt.arl.DeepCopy()\n168: \t\t\tif tt.arl == nil {\n169: \t\t\t\tif copy != nil {\n170: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected nil, got non-nil\")\n171: \t\t\t\t}\n172: \t\t\t\treturn\n173: \t\t\t}\n174: \t\t\tif copy == nil {\n175: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected non-nil, got nil\")\n176: \t\t\t\treturn\n177: \t\t\t}\n178: \t\t\tif len(copy.Items) != len(tt.arl.Items) {\n179: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Items length %d, got %d\", len(tt.arl.Items), len(copy.Items))\n180: \t\t\t}\n181: \t\t})\n182: \t}\n183: }\n184: \n185: func TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopyObject(t *testing.T) {\n186: \tar := &AgentRuntime{\n187: \t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test\"},\n188: \t}\n189: \tobj := ar.DeepCopyObject()\n190: \tif obj == nil {\n191: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected non-nil, got nil\")\n192: \t}\n193: \tif obj.(*AgentRuntime).Name != \"test\" {\n194: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Name 'test', got %s\", obj.(*AgentRuntime).Name)\n195: \t}\n196: }\n197: \n198: func TestCodeInterpreterDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n199: \ttests := []struct {\n200: \t\tname string\n201: \t\tci   *CodeInterpreter\n202: \t}{\n203: \t\t{\n204: \t\t\tname: \"nil\",\n205: \t\t\tci:   nil,\n206: \t\t},\n207: \t\t{\n208: \t\t\tname: \"empty\",\n209: \t\t\tci:   &CodeInterpreter{},\n210: \t\t},\n211: \t\t{\n212: \t\t\tname: \"full\",\n213: \t\t\tci: &CodeInterpreter{\n214: \t\t\t\tTypeMeta: metav1.TypeMeta{\n215: \t\t\t\t\tKind:       CodeInterpreterKind,\n216: \t\t\t\t\tAPIVersion: GroupVersion.String(),\n217: \t\t\t\t},\n218: \t\t\t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n219: \t\t\t\t\tName:      \"test-codeinterpreter\",\n220: \t\t\t\t\tNamespace: \"default\",\n221: \t\t\t\t},\n222: \t\t\t\tSpec: CodeInterpreterSpec{\n223: \t\t\t\t\tPorts: []TargetPort{\n224: \t\t\t\t\t\t{\n225: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tPort:     8080,\n226: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tProtocol: ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n227: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n228: \t\t\t\t\t},\n229: \t\t\t\t\tTemplate: &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{\n230: \t\t\t\t\t\tImage:           \"python:latest\",\n231: \t\t\t\t\t\tImagePullPolicy: corev1.PullIfNotPresent,\n232: \t\t\t\t\t\tLabels: map[string]string{\n233: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"app\": \"code-interpreter\",\n234: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n235: \t\t\t\t\t\tAnnotations: map[string]string{\n236: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\"annotation\": \"value\",\n237: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n238: \t\t\t\t\t\tRuntimeClassName: ptr(\"runc\"),\n239: \t\t\t\t\t\tCommand:          []string{\"python\"},\n240: \t\t\t\t\t\tArgs:             []string{\"-m\", \"app\"},\n241: \t\t\t\t\t\tEnvironment: []corev1.EnvVar{\n242: \t\t\t\t\t\t\t{Name: \"ENV\", Value: \"test\"},\n243: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n244: \t\t\t\t\t\tResources: corev1.ResourceRequirements{\n245: \t\t\t\t\t\t\tLimits: corev1.ResourceList{},\n246: \t\t\t\t\t\t},\n247: \t\t\t\t\t},\n248: \t\t\t\t\tSessionTimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 15 * time.Minute},\n249: \t\t\t\t\tMaxSessionDuration: &metav1.Duration{Duration: 8 * time.Hour},\n250: \t\t\t\t\tWarmPoolSize:       ptrInt32(5),\n251: \t\t\t\t\tAuthMode:           AuthModePicoD,\n252: \t\t\t\t},\n253: \t\t\t\tStatus: CodeInterpreterStatus{\n254: \t\t\t\t\tConditions: []metav1.Condition{\n255: \t\t\t\t\t\t{Type: \"Ready\", Status: metav1.ConditionTrue},\n256: \t\t\t\t\t},\n257: \t\t\t\t\tReady: true,\n258: \t\t\t\t},\n259: \t\t\t},\n260: \t\t},\n261: \t}\n262: \n263: \tfor _, tt := range tests {\n264: \t\tt.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n265: \t\t\tcopy := tt.ci.DeepCopy()\n266: \t\t\tif tt.ci == nil {\n267: \t\t\t\tif copy != nil {\n268: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected nil, got non-nil\")\n269: \t\t\t\t}\n270: \t\t\t\treturn\n271: \t\t\t}\n272: \t\t\tif copy == nil {\n273: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected non-nil, got nil\")\n274: \t\t\t\treturn\n275: \t\t\t}\n276: \t\t\tif copy == tt.ci {\n277: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected different pointer, got same pointer\")\n278: \t\t\t}\n279: \t\t\tif copy.Spec.AuthMode != tt.ci.Spec.AuthMode {\n280: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected AuthMode %s, got %s\", tt.ci.Spec.AuthMode, copy.Spec.AuthMode)\n281: \t\t\t}\n282: \t\t\tif tt.ci.Spec.WarmPoolSize != nil {\n283: \t\t\t\tif *copy.Spec.WarmPoolSize != *tt.ci.Spec.WarmPoolSize {\n284: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected WarmPoolSize %d, got %d\", *tt.ci.Spec.WarmPoolSize, *copy.Spec.WarmPoolSize)\n285: \t\t\t\t}\n286: \t\t\t}\n287: \t\t\tif tt.ci.Spec.Template != nil {\n288: \t\t\t\tif copy.Spec.Template.Image != tt.ci.Spec.Template.Image {\n289: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Template Image %s, got %s\", tt.ci.Spec.Template.Image, copy.Spec.Template.Image)\n290: \t\t\t\t}\n291: \t\t\t\tif len(copy.Spec.Template.Command) != len(tt.ci.Spec.Template.Command) {\n292: \t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Command length %d, got %d\", len(tt.ci.Spec.Template.Command), len(copy.Spec.Template.Command))\n293: \t\t\t\t}\n294: \t\t\t\tif tt.ci.Spec.Template.Labels != nil {\n295: \t\t\t\t\tcopy.Spec.Template.Labels[\"app\"] = \"modified\"\n296: \t\t\t\t\tif tt.ci.Spec.Template.Labels[\"app\"] == \"modified\" {\n297: \t\t\t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"DeepCopy should be deep, modifying copy should not affect original\")\n298: \t\t\t\t\t}\n299: \t\t\t\t}\n300: \t\t\t}\n301: \t\t\tif copy.Status.Ready != tt.ci.Status.Ready {\n302: \t\t\t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Ready %v, got %v\", tt.ci.Status.Ready, copy.Status.Ready)\n303: \t\t\t}\n304: \t\t})\n305: \t}\n306: }\n307: \n308: func TestCodeInterpreterListDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n309: \tcil := &CodeInterpreterList{\n310: \t\tItems: []CodeInterpreter{\n311: \t\t\t{ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"item1\"}},\n312: \t\t\t{ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"item2\"}},\n313: \t\t},\n314: \t}\n315: \tcopy := cil.DeepCopy()\n316: \tif len(copy.Items) != len(cil.Items) {\n317: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Items length %d, got %d\", len(cil.Items), len(copy.Items))\n318: \t}\n319: }\n320: \n321: func TestCodeInterpreterDeepCopyObject(t *testing.T) {\n322: \tci := &CodeInterpreter{\n323: \t\tObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test\"},\n324: \t}\n325: \tobj := ci.DeepCopyObject()\n326: \tif obj == nil {\n327: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected non-nil, got nil\")\n328: \t}\n329: \tif obj.(*CodeInterpreter).Name != \"test\" {\n330: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Name 'test', got %s\", obj.(*CodeInterpreter).Name)\n331: \t}\n332: }\n333: \n334: func TestTargetPortDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n335: \ttp := &TargetPort{\n336: \t\tPathPrefix: \"/api\",\n337: \t\tName:       \"api\",\n338: \t\tPort:       8080,\n339: \t\tProtocol:   ProtocolTypeHTTP,\n340: \t}\n341: \tcopy := tp.DeepCopy()\n342: \tif copy.PathPrefix != tp.PathPrefix {\n343: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected PathPrefix %s, got %s\", tp.PathPrefix, copy.PathPrefix)\n344: \t}\n345: \tif copy.Port != tp.Port {\n346: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Port %d, got %d\", tp.Port, copy.Port)\n347: \t}\n348: }\n349: \n350: func TestSandboxTemplateDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n351: \tst := &SandboxTemplate{\n352: \t\tLabels:      map[string]string{\"label\": \"value\"},\n353: \t\tAnnotations: map[string]string{\"annotation\": \"value\"},\n354: \t\tSpec: corev1.PodSpec{\n355: \t\t\tContainers: []corev1.Container{{Name: \"container\"}},\n356: \t\t},\n357: \t}\n358: \tcopy := st.DeepCopy()\n359: \tcopy.Labels[\"label\"] = \"modified\"\n360: \tif st.Labels[\"label\"] == \"modified\" {\n361: \t\tt.Errorf(\"DeepCopy should be deep, modifying copy should not affect original\")\n362: \t}\n363: }\n364: \n365: func TestCodeInterpreterSandboxTemplateDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n366: \tcist := &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{\n367: \t\tLabels:           map[string]string{\"label\": \"value\"},\n368: \t\tAnnotations:      map[string]string{\"annotation\": \"value\"},\n369: \t\tRuntimeClassName: ptr(\"runc\"),\n370: \t\tImage:            \"python:latest\",\n371: \t\tImagePullPolicy:  corev1.PullIfNotPresent,\n372: \t\tImagePullSecrets: []corev1.LocalObjectReference{{Name: \"secret\"}},\n373: \t\tEnvironment:      []corev1.EnvVar{{Name: \"ENV\", Value: \"val\"}},\n374: \t\tCommand:          []string{\"cmd\"},\n375: \t\tArgs:             []string{\"arg\"},\n376: \t\tResources:        corev1.ResourceRequirements{},\n377: \t}\n378: \tcopy := cist.DeepCopy()\n379: \tif copy.Image != cist.Image {\n380: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected Image %s, got %s\", cist.Image, copy.Image)\n381: \t}\n382: \tcopy.Labels[\"label\"] = \"modified\"\n383: \tif cist.Labels[\"label\"] == \"modified\" {\n384: \t\tt.Errorf(\"DeepCopy should be deep\")\n385: \t}\n386: \t*copy.RuntimeClassName = \"modified\"\n387: \tif *cist.RuntimeClassName == \"modified\" {\n388: \t\tt.Errorf(\"DeepCopy should be deep for RuntimeClassName\")\n389: \t}\n390: }\n391: \n392: func TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n393: \tif AuthModePicoD != \"picod\" {\n394: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected AuthModePicoD to be 'picod', got '%s'\", AuthModePicoD)\n395: \t}\n396: \tif AuthModeNone != \"none\" {\n397: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected AuthModeNone to be 'none', got '%s'\", AuthModeNone)\n398: \t}\n399: }\n400: \n401: func TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n402: \tif ProtocolTypeHTTP != \"HTTP\" {\n403: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected ProtocolTypeHTTP to be 'HTTP', got '%s'\", ProtocolTypeHTTP)\n404: \t}\n405: \tif ProtocolTypeHTTPS != \"HTTPS\" {\n406: \t\tt.Errorf(\"expected ProtocolTypeHTTPS to be 'HTTPS', got '%s'\", ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n407: \t}\n408: }\n409: \n410: func TestJSONSerialization(t *testing.T) {\n411: \ttests := []struct {\n412: \t\tname     string\n413: \t\tobj      runtime.Object\n414: \t\tjsonTags []string\n415: \t}{\n416: \t\t{\n417: \t\t\tname: \"AgentRuntime\",\n418: \t\t\tobj: &AgentRuntime{\n419: \t\t\t\tSpec: AgentRuntimeSpec{\n420: \t\t\t\t\tPorts:              []TargetPort{{Port: 8080}},\n421: \t\t\t\t\tSessionTimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 15 * time.Minute},\n422: \t\t\t\t\tMaxSessionDuration: &metav1.Duration{Duration: 8 * time.Hour},\n423: \t\t\t\t},\n424: \t\t\t},\n425: \t\t\tjsonTags: []string{\"targetPort\", \"podTem